OL,5, Facebook and Instagram are launching   
OL,6, subscriptions in most of Europe that   
OL,7, will remove adverts from the platforms.
OL,9,FPeople using the Meta-owned platforms  
OL,10,Fwill be able to pay 9.99 euros (#8.72) 
OL,11,Fper month for an ad-free experience. It
OL,12,Fwill not be available in the UK.       
OL,14,FIn January, Meta was fined 390m euros  
OL,15,Ffor breaking EU data rules around ads. 
OL,17,FThe regulator said at the time the firm
OL,18,Fcould not "force consent" by saying    
OL,19,Fconsumers must accept how their data is
OL,20,Fused or leave the platforms.           
